What does it do? 

This algo is designed to work an iceberg order. The difference with this order and a regular Iceberg is that if used to Hit/Lift this will attempt to take the maximum size available before it begins iceberging. Where a regular iceberg would continiously iceberg the size available giving market participants the opportunity to withdraw their orders.
